{"tid":1516021,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"超級電腦預測皇馬捧歐聯","createTime":"2019-08-29T11:49:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T13:12:32.000Z","uid":3454,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"d1e72da68885a81d89d506b7b9bac4736f3c1aa6","tid":1516021,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:49:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26654866158\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D26654866158&d=uSpWWhS%2FFNP1%2BK4afk1FkLHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=ca420af3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=26654866158</a><br />\n【Now Sports-體育】BT Sport利用超級電腦預測今季歐聯形勢，結果上季冠軍利物浦無緣衛冕，冠軍又是皇家馬德里！<br />\n<br />\n利物浦連續2季殺入歐聯，前季不敵皇馬，上季則以2:0輕取熱刺，6度封王，但超級電腦認為紅軍今季將輝煌不再。<br />\n<br />\n超級電腦預測英超3雄利物浦、曼城和車路士皆能在分組賽晉級，但英超恐怕很難像上季一樣統治武林，只有紅軍和車仔可以躋身8強，但僅此而已。<br />\n<br />\n「歐聯之王」皇馬被認為會先在8強淘汰車仔，4強上演西班牙國家打吡時力克巴塞隆拿，決賽更以3:2險勝拜仁慕尼黑，再度捧盃。<br />\n<br />\n超級電腦預測今季歐聯戰果<br />\n8強<br />\n皇家馬德里4:2車路士<br />\n巴塞隆拿2:0利物浦<br />\n拜仁慕尼黑3:2巴黎聖日耳門<br />\n祖雲達斯2:1里昂<br />\n<br />\n4強<br />\n皇家馬德里5:2巴塞隆拿<br />\n拜仁慕尼黑3:0祖雲達斯<br />\n<br />\n決賽<br />\n皇家馬德里3:2拜仁慕尼黑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n拖舟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b83b90e53db65ba322c1fbd9d38c5dc2895c1b0","tid":1516021,"uid":144996,"like":53,"dislike":2,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:52:26.000Z","msg":"屌 一場都未踢就俾人燈"},{"pid":"0ffa4f0e5c682373f2f46c0edc0e3551082134d6","tid":1516021,"uid":18925,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T11:53:49.000Z","msg":"牙朗2回合一球都入唔到<br />\n有咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4033a6b3842fe9066fb6213a9f70968d7347e9ac","tid":1516021,"uid":4574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"有c朗皇馬<br />\n<br />\n就話有機"},{"pid":"a3484fd32a5b6e42099bb3e83e5e15e06976c852","tid":1516021,"uid":83